# External Reference Repositories

This directory stores third-party repositories used only for architecture and implementation reference.

- These repositories are not company services.
- Do not treat them as deployable workspace projects.
- Keep source URL, license, ref, and update metadata in `manifest.json`.
- Put open-source clones under `open_source/`.
- Put raw snapshots under `raw/external_reference_repos/`.
- Put curated analysis under `wiki/reference/`.

